        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Introduction to CLUE</strong></p><p>To get started, watch <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SaQK0B_Sinw\">this video</a> to learn more about the CLUE platform. </p><p>After watching the video, add a text tile to your workspace and tell us what are your initial thoughts about the CLUE platform and what questions you have about it. </p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "f_KkdkpBCqi9KRxk",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<h3><strong>Introduction to Dataflow</strong></h3><p>Because these lessons involve engineering and robotics, you will also need a programming tool that can read sensor data and control outputs. In this unit, the programming tool is called Dataflow, and it can be launched from the button with two connected boxes, like this one:</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
