          "url": "brain/images/UIbuttons.jpg",
          "filename": "brain/images/UIbuttons.jpg"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "muWZ2shXQUjLh0Hz",
        "title": "Noticing Differences",
        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "bIswUY",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<li>Look through the other programs your peers made.</li><li>Find one group that connected the gripper to the program differently than your group OR one group who suggested a different strategy for figuring out what blocks do.</li>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 7",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p><strong>Which group:</strong></p><p><strong>What was different about how they connected their gripper, or about their strategy?</strong></p><p><strong>Do you think your way or their way is better for figuring out what blocks do, or were they both equally good? Why?</strong></p>"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "FFsWGlSrLofqnz1h",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<h3>Publishing your workspace </h3><p>When you&#x27;re done with today&#x27;s activities, try publishing your workspace. To do so, click on &quot;Publish Workspace&quot; at the top of your workspace.</p><p>When you publish, your workspace will appear under the pink &quot;Extension&quot; tab above. Student work will go under the Class Models and Data tab. Teacher work will go under the Custom Lessons tab. </p><p>Check if any of your classmates has published their workspace yet. </p><p></p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "9R8Pq1QLUzthSal0",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<h3>Reflection</h3><p>At the end of each lesson, you will be asked to post a brief reflection. Click on the &quot;Reflection&quot; tab to learn more. </p>"
          ]
        }
      }
